snippet.title: Company of Heroes 3 - Fire & Steel Trailer
snippet.description:
Company of Heroes 3: Fire and Steel is a Battlegroup DLC pack consisting of four epic Battlegroups for Multiplayer and Co-Op/Skirmish vs AI. 

Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3469800/Company_of_Heroes_3_Fire__Steel/
